    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The EVM doesn't run if there's no code associated with the recipient of a transaction. \r\n\r\nAs for Solidity, all languages compile down to EVM bytecode and that's what is executed. You can have arbitrary higher level languages all run by the same EVM.",
